{"tid":2010071,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我地不如算啦，timing唔夾，等等下就無哂feel","createTime":"2020-05-10T07:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T07:55:27.000Z","uid":97887,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60148cfcb010ba7d85e90c7cbd72d6693e65298b","tid":2010071,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"那天，你告訴我，你想見我。<br />\n<br />\n我說「不，再等一會兒。」<br />\n<br />\n因為工作關係，我們不能想見就見。<br />\n<br />\n「等多陣，好嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n你走了，沒有理會我。<br />\n<br />\n「我地不如算啦，timing唔夾，等等下就無哂Feel」<br />\n<br />\n我唔信，「都係等多陣者，我唔信感覺會無緣無故消失。」<br />\n<br />\n結果，你走了。<br />\n<br />\n我後悔了，上連登開 post，想尋回你。<br />\n<br />\n《急！忍完屎無哂便意點算？》"},{"pid":"d76238d32c3c0235b0ffbf6ba5c2dc5f37039d22","tid":2010071,"uid":185434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"甘油條<br />\n再唔係就搵人開你後庭苞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（不過一定會花生醬......）"},{"pid":"fd035d7160f6dd35bc582735a070b9f40d40d1a1","tid":2010071,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d76238d32c3c0235b0ffbf6ba5c2dc5f37039d22","tid":2010071,"uid":185434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"甘油條<br />\n再唔係就搵人開你後庭苞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（不過一定會花生醬......）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:55:27.000Z","msg":"柯到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係香蕉呀"}]}